{
  "stem": "12462.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They wanted to go back to Moscow to have some conferences anyway.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they never actually had a part in making that decision.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When they came back to the London negotiations, everybody voted for Nuremberg and the Russians said, well, we'll go along with that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they did insist on having the headquarters of the tribunal be in Berlin, but that was merely a temporary thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The indictment was filed, and the first meeting of the tribunal was held in-- in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then immediately the proceedings were moved to Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nuremberg was in the American area of occupation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the general idea was that the Americans would carry the-- the conspiracy charge, that the defendants were associated as principals or accessories in the commission of these crimes, and that we would have the task of proving that.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was suggested by Judge Nikachenko, the Soviet judge, when they were starting to lay out the way the indictment might be formed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in addition to the conspiracy charge, there would be a charge of the actual waging and preparing for the war, and then a charge on war crimes, which were more or less the traditional kind of crimes, and then crimes against humanity, which included the crimes of oppression and persecution and the kinds of things which were-- had not previously been tried as crimes before tribunals.",
      "word_count": 67
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Americans, given the conspiracy case and having the largest number of staff, actually extended the conspiracy to reach into every part of the case so that by the time-- well, let me back up.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
